Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,Ugy_ciowsQ_99_4cMNx4AaABAg.AWGmqk8WksIAWHaX4xGT2J,Ugy_ciowsQ_99_4cMNx4AaABAg,@thomastimlin1724,"So hard to choose, but I will pick ""Of all the Gin joints in all the towns in all the world...she walks into mine.""  In college around 1978, they played old movies and a bunch of us went to Casablanca. For the next 3 months we were all quoting it and saying certain lines to make each other laugh. One girl, a  vocal major who was a very talented  singer,  in the music  dept where I went, she'd walk into the  student  break room and inevitable some guy would say ""Of all the Gin joints in all the towns in all the world...she walks into mine.""  She  looked confused. Then one day she  found out what was going on. Soon day she  had  an answer, with  her nose in the  air: ""If had known you were here, I wouldn't  have come."" We all burst out laughing at the guy.",2026-05-01T23:06:43Z,2026-05-01T23:09:28Z,3,True,,2026-05-03T02:00:57.127156
