Marrakech,Gqs5eDnyDPM,UgxJjAIjpV_plX1UrZN4AaABAg,,@jgvarea,"Greetings. 
The sweets you show at 9:15 are mass-produced and don't represent the exquisite Moroccan pastry.
They contain more peanuts than almonds and sugary syrups instead of honey, and the flours are usually of poor quality.
To enjoy true Moroccan pastries, you have to go to Pastiseria Le Gato in Marrakech, among many others; they're nothing like what you find in the souks.",2026-02-06T13:25:05Z,2026-02-06T13:25:05Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-03T02:01:27.897498
